1. *Spremna* sam da počnem. (I am ready to start.)
2. Spremni smo da se pomerimo. (We are ready to move.)
3. *Spremno* sam pratila njegove instrukcije. (I followed his instructions willingly.)
4. Njegova služba je *spremna* da nam pomogne. (His service is ready to help us.)
5. *Spremnije* od ostalih je ispunila uslove. (She fulfilled the conditions more readily than the others.)